<h2>Affix Mixin</h2>
<p>Affix behaviour can be mixed in to any widget. Simply use the <code>affix</code> attibute</p>
<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <div style="height: 300px">
        <w-toggle-button class="affix-example" affix viewport-offset-top="100">
            Affixed toggle
        </w-toggle-button>
    </div>
</div>
